.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-FUNDING-AGE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-funding-age \- FEAT-2050 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-funding-age
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-funding-age for lightning CLI (FEAT-2050).
.PP
Reports the age in seconds of the funding transaction for each peer channel
by querying listpeerchannels. Uses opened_at or created_at timestamps when
available.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
